snippet.title: ACDev
snippet.description:
My name is Adam Chandler and this channel is all about the ins and outs of Game Development. I create game-dev tutorials using Unity and Unreal with a programming emphasis, but not exclusive to programming! I also enjoy talking about Sound Design and Aesthetic as well, so be on the lookout for those videos. We'll explore a good mix of basic, intermediate and advanced concepts in these videos, though I always try to build even the advanced concepts from the basics.

The goal of this channel is to give an in depth breakdown of concepts while we look at practical examples. I believe it's much better for videos to explain things clearly as we go, rather than just be a quick list of buttons to click. This means that the videos may be a bit longer... but that's because they're packed with content!

You can find my longer tutorial topic series in the Playlists Tab, so feel free to start browsing!
